title: Corrections & Amplifications
text:
---

The Computer History Museum is in Mountain View, Calif. A Nov. 26 obituary for Frederick P. Brooks Jr. incorrectly said it is based in the U.K.

(See: "Obituaries: IBM Executive Managed Seminal Computer System" -- WSJ Nov. 26, 2022)

---

Hurricane Nicole made landfall near Vero Beach, Fla. A Nov. 12 U.S. Watch article about the storm incorrectly said it made landfall near Wilbur-by-the-Sea, Fla.

(See: "U.S. News: U.S. Watch" -- WSJ Nov. 12, 2022)

---

Readers can alert The Wall Street Journal to any errors in news articles by e-mailing wsjcontact@wsj.com or by calling 888-410-2667.
